meanings: [Noun] A person supposed to have paranormal abilities.
[Noun] A person who practices the development of psychic ability.
A being of passive psych power. Having been around for at least 12 millenia the consciousnous of previous life trickles into the new bearers aura.
A human being born capable of using telepathy and other paranormal mental abilities. Alternative spelling: ESPer ESP stands for "Extra Sensory Perception".
